Jupyter配置
史上最全Jupyter Lab 配置:
https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_41571493/article/details/88830458

一、Jupyter Lab 安装
	pip install jupyterlab
	pip install ipython

	ipython环境中：配置密码：
	from notebook.auth import passwd
	passwd()
	修改 JupyterLab 配置文件：
		jupyter lab --generate-config

	修改以下配置：

		c.NotebookApp.allow_root = True
		c.NotebookApp.open_browser = False
		c.NotebookApp.password = '刚才复制的输出粘贴到这里来'

	下载npm:
		https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/


二、nodejs通过nvm来安装：
	https://www.cnblogs.com/musings/p/8976074.html

		1、wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.0/install.sh | bash
		2、重启：Xshell
		3、command -v nvm
		4、nvm ls
		5、nvm ls-remote
		6、nvm install 10.8.0
		7、node -v
